Let delta denote the transition function and delta-hat denote the extended transition function of the epsilon-NFA whose transition table is given below:

       epsilon    a       b
q0:    {q0}      {q1}    {}
q1:    {}        {}      {q2}
q2:    {}        {}      {}
q3:    {}        {}      {q2}

Then delta-hat(q0, aba) is
A. {}
B. {q0, q1}
C. {q2}
D. {q0, q1, q2}
